# TECH STACK

## Frontend
- React 18 + TypeScript
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion for all animations
- Recharts for the attribution ring

## Data
- All simulated - no real blockchain yet
- WebSocket from backend OR internal React simulation loop
- No localStorage or sessionStorage ever

## Design Tokens
- Background: #030712
- Primary green (satoshis): #00ff88
- Purple (contribution scored): #7c3aed  
- Red (decaying): #ef4444
- Gold (external attribution): #f59e0b
- Font numbers: JetBrains Mono
- Font text: Inter

## The Gold Color Is Sacred
#f59e0b is ONLY used for external/advocacy contributions
"The agent found them" moments are always gold
Never use gold for anything else
